      },
      "date": "2012-08-03 16:27:25.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPS: this shouldn't have requested landing from Gerit Gatekeeper until it had received the required positive reviews, and also it needs a proper LU Jira ticket number.",
